Residents of Ndimu  village  in Elburgon area in Nakuru were today taken aback after  an  eleven  year  old   boy committed  suicide. According  to  neighbors  the  deceased’s family, the boy is said to have  committed  suicide  after   his  mother  left  to  attend prayers at a local church brings  to three  the  number of  minors  who  have  committed  suicide in  the  area  this  year alone.  